Marketing Coordinator
BAC Middle East
JLT, UAE
Posted on: 30 Apr 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
AED7000 Inclusive of HRA and Transport
On behalf of our client a British Exhibition company that is based in Dubai we are looking to recruit a Marketing Coordinator.
Reporting to the Marketing Manager you will be responsible for keeping an accurate spreadsheet of marketing contra deals and maintaining both soft and hard copies of media deals, liaise with media partners regarding exhibition stands, distribute press releases to media partners and other duties deemed suitable
REQUIREMENTS
The successful candidate must be a resident of the UAE, be degree educated to MBA level in a marketing discipline, have MS Word and Excel experience, strong attention to deal with fluency in both written and spoken
English
ABOUT THE COMPANY
BAC Middle East - the longest established professional recruitment consultancy in the UAE. Established in 1979, we have been at the forefront of the region's recruitment industry for 30 years and were the first firm of our type in the world to achieve ISO9001 certification: a reflection of our constant emphasis on quality and customer satisfaction.
With our well-developed infrastructure and staff strength, we are able to assist you with recruitment needs ranging from junior professionals through to middle and senior management, whatever your industry sector.
BAC's proven regional experience and resources can help ensure that you recruit the best available candidates and enjoy the many advantages of a managed recruitment process.
